{"tid":2171251,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"你知道英文字母的順序嗎？","createTime":"2020-08-23T20:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T21:02:03.000Z","uid":59818,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f358aefbd855c90445691c81fa859b95a81f7fb2","tid":2171251,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T20:54:50.000Z","msg":"巴塞隆拿發表聲明，指尼馬獲准豁免操練，將在日內赴巴黎聖日耳門體檢，料以破世界轉會費紀錄2.22億歐元（約20.55億港元）轉戰法甲。尼馬在加泰羅尼亞市機場接受了法國Nineup報獨家專訪，透露無法上位成為一哥，是他決定離開球會的主因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/040749_d50608616a9827d73c08791473884943.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F040749_d50608616a9827d73c08791473884943.jpg&h=a7aba570&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「巴塞有一名老大哥，他決定球會用那個領隊、購入那些球員、踢甚麼陣式和那位球員正選，我們總活在陰影之下。」沒有指名道姓，尼馬卻娓娓道出有人這些年來幾乎主宰了球會所有決策。<br />\n<br />\n尼馬回憶上月與老大哥的對話：「記得上個月跟他在酒吧聊天，談起球會來季目標，我預告自己今年將會大爆發，為球會重奪聯賽和歐聯。」<br />\n<br />\n「老大哥沒有回應，望著酒杯問我：『你知道英文字母的順序嗎？』我說當然知道，然後他就說：『N永遠排在M後面，這是定律，即使你成功，亦是在我的允許之下。』」<br />\n<br />\n「瞬間我明白了他意思了，他要永遠當球會的老大哥。於是我不忿地回應了一句：『那麼C排在M的前面又代表甚麼呢？』他馬上就黑面了，自此我們就沒有再說過話。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/040958_df7985dfc89d5fe7151dbd8d7595a3b9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F040958_df7985dfc89d5fe7151dbd8d7595a3b9.png&h=2761de48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這時助手催促上機，尼馬最後向記者道：「我要起程往巴黎了，你還有甚麼問題嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n記者：「沒有了，剛好口袋有一包M&amp;M朱古力，送給你上機吃吧。」<br />\n<br />\n尼馬接過朱古力後苦笑：「看吧，連朱古力也是只有M沒有N，他媽的。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/040809_0f87c64f7679ff9b2802c30ae8eb3d59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F040809_0f87c64f7679ff9b2802c30ae8eb3d59.png&h=b309b031&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76fb765b87aecfede39e6c1e954ae9bd435a6867","tid":2171251,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T20:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ac7210473c9ae28dd62b4cffd2dd491e564fa5","tid":2171251,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T20:56:39.000Z","msg":"C&gt;L&gt;M&gt;N"},{"pid":"ade53624dfef28a758f5e2c5141e31636a15c80b","tid":2171251,"uid":54712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T20:56:44.000Z","msg":"佢唔走既話羅馬同利記個次都應該拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8fe98a471d394869ef1f8e55abe2285b75126d","tid":2171251,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ade53624dfef28a758f5e2c5141e31636a15c80b","tid":2171251,"uid":54712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T20:56:44.000Z","msg":"佢唔走既話羅馬同利記個次都應該拎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T20:58:54.000Z","msg":"要做世一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe61dac1ae45c5bc4062291f4a5856190ab4ef31","tid":2171251,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:01:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc54212600853fe8b4d382cc65cada9f041bd383","tid":2171251,"uid":5123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T21:02:03.000Z","msg":"Alexis&gt;C&gt;M&gt;N"}]}